Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:09.27,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,When we were kids, there was a \Ntime that Manaka and I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.80,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We had gone to the \Noutskirts of the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.48,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,into the outer sea to look for coral,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:19.63,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and gotten so wrapped up that we \Ncouldn't find the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:31.80,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we got hungry, tired of walking,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.00,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and on the verge of tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.25,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The one who appeared in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.15,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,was Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.48,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Without saying a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.88,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari just kept pulling on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:51.18,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I clearly remember \Nhis eyes focused straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:55.95,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,in front of him and the feeling \Nof him holding my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:58.01,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.33,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I was too \Nsurprised when I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.08,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,that Hikari had found Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:09.01,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I think I knew somewhere in my \Nheart that it would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:14.94,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought somewhere in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.28,0:01:20.30,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,that if someone were able to \Ndo that, it'd only be Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.02,Episode-Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Nineteen: \N The Lost, Lost Little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.82,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:04.25,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, taking care \Nof her here should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.57,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:10.54,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've been examining \Nher since yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:15.14,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd have to say that she's pretty healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.43,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with \Nher brain waves, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.49,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,and judging from you two \Nwho have already woken up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.76,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,she should wake up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:25.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And her Ena may grow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm just glad \Nthat Manaka's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You think that, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.41,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.59,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You little... Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, Chisaki, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.58,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,So lively... how nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.73,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kancho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You fool! Like I'd keep \Nfalling for the same attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.14,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, she won't be \Nable to stay asleep either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Special move: kancho reversal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.67,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,This is so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.13,Main,akira,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kancho reversal reversal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:01.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari... Must be really \Nhappy that he found Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.48,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.47,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,Hiradaira-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:14.88,Main,doc,0000,0000,0000,,you can just have your self-study log in\Nto me by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:15.77,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:24.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've \Nseen you in your nurse outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.45,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.18,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I almost didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't gotten used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.12,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it just feels like \NI'm just wearing the outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.07,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here, \Nwant to have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.41,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I will, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,hurry and wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The Ofunehiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Both Dad and Uroko-sama \Nsaid it'd be useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:01.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hoping for \Nsomething the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.25,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hoping that something would happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,wanting something to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And then something like \Nthat ended up happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:13.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Did you save Akari back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What happened back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you had something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:22.05,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,to tell me after the Ofunehiki \Nwas over, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, no matter how \Nfar I reached for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't reach you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:35.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But now even if you want me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.32,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.50,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan also likes Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.38,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:04.06,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Putting her all into caring for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.63,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but not being able to \Ntake the next step...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.09,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I always just thought of her as a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.89,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:15.24,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She's now the same age \Nas we were back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.13,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:25.35,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost the same age as \NAkari-san was back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:29.03,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You still worried about the \Ngirlie from the sea village?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.05,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:34.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she'll wake up soon, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:37.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She lost some of her Ena, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.48,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Her Ena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:47.55,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You said she was found sleeping at a \Ngraveyard of Ojoshi-samas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.51,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:56.35,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,There's a continuation to the story \Nabout the Sea God and Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.82,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Continuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.02,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many who'll talk about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:05.91,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,because it's a story with a sad ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.15,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't talked since \Nyou got back, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.10,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.67,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.25,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Chisaki, \Nhow's Manaka doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:35.34,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't had a \Nchance to go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:36.64,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said that there's \Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.93,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Now you guys will have \Nmore data to conceal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Conceal"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.53,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently both Mihashi-sensei \Nand Tsumugu aren't going to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.67,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,officially present the \Ndetails about the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:59.54,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,that we were able to get into Shioshishio \Nor about Miuna-chan for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.79,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.06,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.09,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Mihashi-sensei will put \Nit all in a thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.78,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Then he'll send it to \Nan academic journal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,and the official presentation\Ncomes after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:10.28,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.67,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, I, and Miuna-chan didn't dive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:18.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,to Shioshishio and put our lives in \Ndanger for the sake of your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.40,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:23.06,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason for that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.76,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,If the thesis isn't acknowledged,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.54,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,we won't receive funding anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,All his research to avert disaster
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.44,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,from occurring on the surface\Nby establishing the link
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:37.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,between the abnormal weather\Nand the sea village will cease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.74,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And then the media will \Nalso get involved and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.62,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna will go through a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:47.83,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:51.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu, you never explain enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.90,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.15,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give him a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There is a lot going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:03.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an adult, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.92,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.11,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.11,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.94,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"An adult," huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.80,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.96,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,How nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.99,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.41,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.37,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:17.76,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki, the bath is getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.81,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.42,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki, I'm opening the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:47.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,H-How long are you going \Nto stare, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.83,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.99,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.73,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:26.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.54,Pickled Shallots,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Pickled Shallots
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.54,Red Chile Oil,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chile Oil
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.54,Soy Marinated,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Marinated in Soy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:34.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I was just looking \Nfor Grandpa's plum wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.74,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the mood to drink some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.15,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm an adult and \Nsome lonely housewife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.72,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.43,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.77,Plum Juice,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Plum Wine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:04.14,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you're \Nsupposed to drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that alcohol tastes \Nbetter when you're an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.75,Plum Juice Without Shochu,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Plum Juice Without Shochu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.75,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that after \Njust drinking this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just plum \Nwine, alcohol is alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:20.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... plum wine is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Quit trying to act like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.24,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:49.15,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see what \NShioshishio looks like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.88,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:13:01.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari was talking to \NManaka while she slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:06.43,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't much of a shock, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:13.19,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to \Nhave eyes like that ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:17.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,My body got all big on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:20.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and yet things are spilling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:26.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Does becoming an adult mean \Nyou lose a lot of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.83,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You probably do lose a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:36.21,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But that just means you need fulfill \Nwhat you lost with new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:56.77,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Our time together these five \Nyears has been like that for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.86,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You don't plan on doing anything \Nmore than that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.35,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But we need to get her to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.54,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.58,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.93,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I never did tell you, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.42,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.01,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,My gratitude for saving \Nme at the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.61,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.26,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something to thank me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.01,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm not being modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.65,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, it really \Ncrossed my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.48,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,"If I just overlook it, you'll disappear."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:42.30,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,"And then I'll be able \Nto be with Chisaki."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.67,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't save him."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.47,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,"Just abandon him."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.12,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But you dove in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.87,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:52.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,if you were able to just \Noverlook something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.56,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never let you have Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.69,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,So the truth comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:57.87,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.55,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.13,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I really am grateful that \Nyou guys came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:07.10,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Things were suspended this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.90,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Now both Chisaki and I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.77,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,can move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:25.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I drank quite a bit, but I \Ndidn't get a hangover at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:34.03,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,From this point, I dive \Ndown seven meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:34.03,shioshishio,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,How to get to Shioshishio
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.89,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I have to face it one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.04,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.00,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being swept away a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.77,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.99,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.35,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.81,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:45.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but at times, you end up \Nbeing really reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:54.96,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,If we're able to get in now, \Nof course I'd come to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:56.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:01.86,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,When he held me back \Nthere, it surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.21,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't feel rugged at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:09.67,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,unlike the men I have to \Ntouch during self-study...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.36,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.76,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Because his smile, his body, \Nand his heart are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:18.43,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly the same as you \Nwere five years ago... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.37,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:25.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,For you, the Ofunehiki \Nwas really recent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:29.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.70,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the normal Chisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:37.27,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had changed quite a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:43.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You still look like you're listening \Nand yet not listening at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.45,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:49.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the fact that you get pissed \Noff when I tease you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:54.99,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here \Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:18:01.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wondering why
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka's Ena's disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:13.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might figure something out\Nif I went back to where we found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.67,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:20.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if this will help or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:23.95,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but Tsumugu's grandfather \Ntold me a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:27.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The continuation of the story \Nabout the Sea God and Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Continuation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:35.10,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,The girl that married the Sea \NGod eventually had children,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.99,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,and their descendants flourished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.09,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,However, as more time passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:44.60,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,it's said that the girl became \Nmore and more depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:51.87,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Because the girl had left behind \Nsomeone she loved on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.36,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the man she loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:59.25,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,she was never able to \Nforget about the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:03.05,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,After finding that out, the Sea God
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:06.46,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,did everything he could \Nto make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:11.00,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, she wasn't able \Nto forget about the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.57,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,so the Sea God had no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.84,Flashback,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,but to let her go\Nback to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.36,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Taking something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:28.52,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it... \Nbut that might be Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ojoshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:46.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,in return for going to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.11,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.89,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa also said that\Nthis was just oral lore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.84,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so he's not sure if it's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:56.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:57.82,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.55,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find him and catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Catch him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:11.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he knows whether\N this story is true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's true, he may \Nknow what needs to be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was at a loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but now I know what I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Chisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:28.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But man, the Sea God \Nis such a selfish jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.99,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Taking people's Ena because \Nthey don't obey him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and randomly giving people Ena...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What is he, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.83,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.16,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even after living hundreds \Nand thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.63,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,he might not have changed at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.35,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that probably has \Nnothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:50.68,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about position \Nor age, but how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.11,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Feel"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm excited for Manaka to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about \Nher Ena no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:01.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and then help Tsumugu with the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.93,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:34.52,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I still do like Hikari after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.88,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,And so, now that Manaka has returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:46.53,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,our time that was frozen for the last \Nfive years finally started moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:50.08,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.20,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.13,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even after a week had passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:59.21,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1055)}there were no signs that \NManaka would awaken at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:31.84,Main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:35.02,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't princes do that often? \NKiss the sleeping princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:36.76,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,How dull...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:37.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they don't want her to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.14,Episode-Title - Copy,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Twenty: \N The Sleeping Princess
